snippet.textDisplay: Rumi said that "You are the universe in an ecstatic motion". When I listen and see  performances like this I can feel his revelation is so true. The best thing I like about Quawallis is that they have the ability to move people . Both physically and spiritually. We have bcome so  accustomed to see physical performances and theatrics on stage. But these legendary singers prove that there is beauty in simplicity. One can move people without moving their bodies much. One can catch the attention of the people without much glitz and glamour. Thanks to coke studio for bringing such gems to us 🙏
